Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:43.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘却了创造　这里将被光明抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来倾吐希望　让不满爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:47.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}吹响革新的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我要全力攀登　再不让他人企及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:58.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突破血雨腥风　让他们全都辟易
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:03.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绝对的控制　将令我咽喉干渴无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:08.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却无法夺去我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让一切感官嘶吼激昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不把炽热的情感寄托在音符中唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:21.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}怎会令心脏热血滚烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:26.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We must be the change we wish to see
