Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:58.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}响彻青天的霹雳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:01.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}闪光掠过的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:09.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无声无息　阴影迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:12.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}尔虞我诈　逐渐失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:16.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}以眼还眼　互相争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:20.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}逐渐磨损本该保护的正以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:23.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}也绝对不会赢得任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:27.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}在笼中仰望到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}雨过天晴眩目的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:34.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}不甘永远被囚禁于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:37.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}哪怕要让我舍弃过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:41.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}要遵从之物仅有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:44.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}本能激发着无穷动力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无论如何都要做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:51.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}因为改变对我是难题
